"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-david-wise-ski-halfpipe-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"For years, people have asked David Wise how long he thinks he can make a career out of halfpipe skiing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wise_(composer)\", \"score\": 0.4456146524189075, \"rank\": 0.6398221343875826, \"text\": \"David Wise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wise_(composer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wise_(composer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 4, \"to\": 9}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 11, \"to\": 17}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 71, \"to\": 79}, {\"ngram\": \"halfpipe skiing\", \"from\": 87, \"to\": 102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always said, I do not know how long I can do this for,\\\" Wise said.\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will let you know when I get there.\\\"\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's almost there.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise, an Olympic gold medalist in 2014 and 2018 and silver medalist in 2022, is in his last Olympic cycle.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 244}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medalist\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"2014 and 2018 and silver medalist\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"his last Olympic cycle\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He plans to retire after either the 2026 Milan Cortina Games (he must still qualify for the deep U.S. team) or, should he tack it on, a less-intense farewell 2026-27 season.\", \