rom\": 716, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"a cost\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While I think I have the best job in the world, my kids and wife pay the price because I am gone a lot.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best job\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"my kids\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"wife\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we definitely did some soul-searching and dug deep.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was honest, and I said I do not feel like my fuel tank is empty.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fuel tank\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I still love this job.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this job\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to do something to keep the lights on in the house.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the lights\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to try to do this one more time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this one more time\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Dec. 7, Wise made his first ski halfpipe podium in nearly two years.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dec.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"his first ski halfpipe podium\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly two years\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This weekend, he competes at the Toyota U.S. Grand Prix at Copper Mountain.An NBC Sports and Peacock broadcast schedule is here.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota_Racing_(Formula_One_team)\", \"score\": 0.9992194706773534, \"rank\": 0.0005560804145001503, \"text\": \"Toyota\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota_Racing_(Formula_One_team)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota_Racing_(Formula_One_team)\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999946708158, \"rank\": 5.271066632039799e-09, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999853525879, \"rank\": 1.4621774883728698e-08, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copper Mountain\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise is one of, if not the last active freeskier who knows what it's like to compete on the sport's highest level before that level was the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's highest level\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He made his Winter X Games debut in 2011, six months before the IOC announced that ski halfpipe and ski slopestyle were added to the Olympic program for the 2014 Sochi Games.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.864154207022385e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Winter X Games\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"ski halfpipe\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"ski slopestyle\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic program\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2014 Sochi Games\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise is the only freeskier to win gold at two Olympics and the only American man to win two golds and a silver across all skiing events.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998509509372359, \"rank\": 0.0001125981284738463, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympics\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"all skiing events\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2022 Beijing Games, he was edged out for gold by Nico Porteous of New Zealand.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.403186446247457, \"rank\": 0.7812545553055321, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Beijing Games\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"Nico Porteous\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In January 2023, he won the X Games for his first major title in five years.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"the X Games\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"his first major title\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two months later, he tore his right ACL in what was already planned to be the last run of his 2022-23 season at the World Championships.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\", \"score\": 0.9964924277141018, \"rank\": 0.003519918655036285, \"text\": \"ACL\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q39888\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last run\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"his 2022-23 season\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kind of was staring the sunset of my career in the face anyway, and then I had sustained another super long-term recovery injury,\\\" said Wise, who broke the femur in the same leg in 2019.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sunset\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"another super long-term recovery injury\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the femur\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"the same leg\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was kind of asking myself and asking God and asking my family, is this the indication?\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"the indication\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never wanted to be in denial when it came time to retire.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"denial\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not ever want to be in denial about it.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"denial\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So some of that was just me being honest with myself.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do I want to fight?\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do I want to work my ass off and come back from this injury and try to stay relevant and try to make another Olympic team?\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my ass\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"this injury\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"another Olympic team\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or do I want to take this as an excuse to retire and still heal my knee and be a functioning athletic human, but not a high-level athlete ever again?\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an excuse\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"my knee\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2723}, {\"ngram\": \"a functioning athletic human\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"not a high-level athlete\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I just do not.\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't born with quit in me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quit\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wise returned for the 2023-24 season, which he called the least successful of his career results-wise.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023-24 season\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"his career results\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was 100% physically recovered but never felt confident.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not finish on the podium across six events.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"six events\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This fall, Wise was joined by daughter Nayeli for his preseason training in Europe for the first time.\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"daughter\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"his preseason training\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she had pigtails, she used to think every skier on TV was her dad.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pigtails\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3192}, {\"ngram\": \"every skier\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"her dad\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's almost more of a travel buddy,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a travel buddy\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's not as dependent on me for her everyday, momentary needs.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her everyday, momentary needs\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I just feel really fortunate to still be able to do what I do for a living and kind of include the family as much as I can.\\\"\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a living\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3434}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then on Dec. 7, Wise placed third in his season debut in China as part of a historic podium.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3543, \"end\": 3548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7021472959811361, \"rank\": 0.2248132321972907, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dec.\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"Wise\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"his season debut\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic podium\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only was ita U.S. sweep, but it was also made up of three men in their 30s for the first time in Worl